org.raistlic.common.predicate

Class Predicates

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.raistlic.common.predicate.Predicates

  • public final class Predicates
extends java.lang.Object
    The class is a collection of static factory methods that creates and exports different types of Predicate instances.
    Since:
    1.3
